{"tid":1012100,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"［跪求日本高手救我］第一次去日本京阪交通一問","createTime":"2019-02-07T09:55:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-07T19:16:01.000Z","uid":167326,"like":0,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"8897ae09e335412163a52a0b816fa0228eef486c","tid":1012100,"uid":167326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T09:55:48.000Z","msg":"路向大概如下<br />\n<br />\n我去6日5夜<br />\n主要住係大阪<br />\n頭2日係大阪行<br />\n但途中可能有2日犯賤想去京都行下 <br />\n但都會即日來回 第日再去過<br />\n最後兩日再留係大阪隨便行買下野<br />\n<br />\nD1 大阪<br />\nD2 大阪<br />\nD3 大阪-&gt;京都-&gt;大阪<br />\nD4 大阪-&gt;京都-&gt;大阪<br />\nD5 大阪<br />\nD6 大阪<br />\n<br />\n問題就黎啦 我睇過有啲人就話買地鐵pass又話巴士pass 又話 jr pass <br />\n<br />\n如果係呢個情況有冇一張野解決哂我所有問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我查左好多資料爬左好多文 但都好亂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12e03bb9dd494574c0914e191386b741229a5482","tid":1012100,"uid":178800,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T09:59:44.000Z","msg":"我第一次去都係同你一樣煩呢樣野,煩好耐,主要係想慳錢<br />\n之後再去京阪,就決定唔慳,一張西瓜卡搞掂,唔再理貴幾多,但起碼唔使心煩"},{"pid":"23519a4adb303877e643c7f2ece187c6aa239dfc","tid":1012100,"uid":167326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"12e03bb9dd494574c0914e191386b741229a5482","tid":1012100,"uid":178800,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T09:59:44.000Z","msg":"我第一次去都係同你一樣煩呢樣野,煩好耐,主要係想慳錢<br />\n之後再去京阪,就決定唔慳,一張西瓜卡搞掂,唔再理貴幾多,但起碼唔使心煩"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T10:01:13.000Z","msg":"西瓜卡？ 啫係日本八達通？ 我查下先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f9cd2875de56ecb2234c3f3777caeedfdfbb12d","tid":1012100,"uid":134778,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T10:02:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"55bb40ed87811ab517bdabe6b02b45108b55cdd3","tid":1012100,"uid":13