3:45.000Z","msg":"巴打介唔介意講吓住邊同去邊度<br />\n因爲如果想去USJ住大阪環狀線附近會方便好多"},{"pid":"eff1c64e1535f391db42c69c89fb5cfa48448805","tid":1012100,"uid":36670,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T10:35:26.000Z","msg":"大阪真係有咁多野行咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n京都景點就多數5點收皮，完左再去 shopping咪一流囉<br />\n京都真係幾多日都玩唔晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n睇你住邊，近心齋橋我就會搭京阪電車<br />\n近梅田我就會搭阪急<br />\n佢地d 2日pass好抵屌，差唔多半價<br />\n同時京都d站位又靚好多<br />\n<br />\n京都入面就都係坐巴士架喇，地鐵好多地方都去唔到<br />\n一日pass先500yen度，成日都成車大陸大媽，佢地都識你地無可能唔識搭既"},{"pid":"b4513a0dff784a59435700aab512e0bab84f773f","tid":1012100,"uid":36670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"804bae2bfd1bc2f9859c149374ad1aa9baa46654","tid":1012100,"uid":119807,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T10:13:27.000Z","msg":"關西個張叫ICOCA，不過都係一樣，日本八達通，絕大部大車站都用到。<br />\n如果你主要係大阪，而又係坐地鐵多，可以考慮買地鐵pass。<br />\n<br />\n下面係JR Pass相關資訊，自己睇下有無岩你用口既<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.westjr.co.jp/global/tc/ticket/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.westjr.co.jp%2Fglobal%2Ftc%2Fticket%2F&d=HNFwsad0YdNlvWXbC%2BF%2BchnxOJLX742lx1SCoot1iYY%3D&h=5c09028d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.westjr.co.jp/global/tc/ticket/</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T10:35:58.000Z","msg":"齋去大阪京都就唔洗坐JR啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"690cfc8e4c7c01db1c5b3b1bc0fc4ea42c994344","tid":1012100,"uid":207462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b4513a0dff784a59435700aab512e0bab84f773f","tid":1012100,"uid":36670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"804bae2bfd1bc2f9859c149374ad1aa9baa46654","tid":1012100,"uid":119807,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T10:13:27.000Z","msg":"關西個張叫ICOCA，不過都係一樣，日本八達通，絕大部大車站都用到。<br />\n如果你主要係大阪，而又係坐地鐵多，可以考慮買地鐵pass。<br />\n<br />\n下面係JR Pass相關資訊，自己睇下有無岩你用口既<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.westjr.co