ike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T09:55:48.000Z","msg":"路向大概如下<br />\n<br />\n我去6日5夜<br />\n主要住係大阪<br />\n頭2日係大阪行<br />\n但途中可能有2日犯賤想去京都行下 <br />\n但都會即日來回 第日再去過<br />\n最後兩日再留係大阪隨便行買下野<br />\n<br />\nD1 大阪<br />\nD2 大阪<br />\nD3 大阪-&gt;京都-&gt;大阪<br />\nD4 大阪-&gt;京都-&gt;大阪<br />\nD5 大阪<br />\nD6 大阪<br />\n<br />\n問題就黎啦 我睇過有啲人就話買地鐵pass又話巴士pass 又話 jr pass <br />\n<br />\n如果係呢個情況有冇一張野解決哂我所有問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我查左好多資料爬左好多文 但都好亂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T10:45:33.000Z","msg":"Yes. But don&rsquo;t expect that to be less expensive. Kyoto is poorly covered by JR pass. <br />\n<br />\nThe benefit of a JR pass would be the ability to take Shinkansen between Osaka and Kyoto which means that it&rsquo;s a 15 minutes ride from Shin-Osaka. If you live in a hotel in Shin-Osaka or Umeda then you can potentially do without a place of stay in Kyoto (but you may wish to stay at the hotels in Kyoto just for the sake of it). <br />\n<br />\nIf you have already booked hotels then I would recommend without a rail pass. Just use icoca."},{"pid":"c92a63298e62b9a462c984d3e0b4c21b3eb1e1e9","tid":1012100,"uid":207462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7e49995104149f8fbe82c8ae756821df461f93c1","tid":1012100,"uid":167326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c385ea5f09d8e9fb03cacc88429554ccadb9b9d3","tid":1012100,"uid":207462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8939b7a9a6ec821eb85b43c248714d8c62259abc","tid":1012100,"uid":167326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T10:29:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 即刻查下咩黎先"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T10:33:45.000Z","msg":"巴打介唔介意講吓住邊同去邊度<br />\n因爲如果想去USJ住大阪環狀線附近會方便好多"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T10:42:50.000Z","msg":"我未決定到住邊呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 就係睇睇下住宿發現唔對路 想決定左交通行程先"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T10:46:24.000Z","msg":"咁一係睇咗想去邊度先啦<br />\n京阪神地區交通有好多選擇<br />\n上面位巴打都有簡單咁講吓<br />\n我自己第一次去連Icoca都冇買直接每次買飛就算<br />\n京都往返大阪除非你搭新幹線<br />\n否則都唔會貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59f33f7904f83c5bde1146a09068d8d9be20318b","tid":1012100,"uid":36670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8897ae09e335412163a52a0b816fa0228eef486c","tid":1012100,"uid":167326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T09:55:48.000Z","msg":"路向大概如下<br />\n<br />\n我去6日5夜<br />\n主要住係大阪<br />\n頭2日係大阪行<br />\n但途中可能有2日犯賤想去京都行下 <br />\n但都會即日來回 第日再去過<br />\n最後兩日再留係大阪隨便行買下野<br />\n<br />\nD1 大阪<br />\nD2 大阪<br />\nD3 大阪-&gt;京都-&gt;大阪<br />\nD4 大阪-&gt;京都-&gt;大阪<br />\nD5 大阪<br />\nD6 大阪<br />\n<br />\n問題就黎啦 我睇過有啲人就話買地鐵pass又話巴士pass 又話 jr pass <br />\n<br />\n如果係呢個情況有冇一張野解決哂我所有問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我查左好多資料爬左好多文 但都好亂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T10:48:00.000Z","msg":"一張解決唔到所有問題<br />\n你好有錢當然可以直接入錢落icoca<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n就咁睇你既行程<br />\n你會需要<br />\n1. 大阪周遊卡2日<br />\n2. 京阪電車/阪急電車2日pass<br />\n3. 京都巴士一日券<br />\n4. 一張icoca"},{"pid":"8a2d5b988a0a42d629b15dd7656169254fa0c0f5","tid":1012100,"uid":207462,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"18ef5b3c3dcfcec4507df14ec2cdc3d31e4d5321","tid":1012100,"uid":80607,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"8897ae09e335412163a52a0b816fa0228eef486c","tid":1012100,"uid":167326,"like":0,"dislik